Salmonella typhimurium DT104, global prevalence (03) 980303222310
Salmonella typhimurium DT104, global prevalence (04) 980306215145
Date: Wed, 25 Mar 1998 11:42:35 -0500
From: Petersen, Kenneth <Kenneth.Petersen@usda.gov>

A report titled "Salmonella Typhimurium DT104 Situation Assessment" is
available at:
<http://www.usda.gov/fsis/ophs/stdt104.htm>
Prepared for USDA/FSIS management, the report summarizes animal and human
epidemiology, and economic impact of this emerging pathogen. An interagency
group will address the recommendations in the report through interaction
with university and government scientists.
--
Kenneth Petersen, DVM, MPH
USDA/FSIS
Office of Public Health and Science
Emerging Pathogens and Zoonotic Diseases Division
Washington, DC
e-mail: kenneth.petersen@usda.gov
[Apart from some distracting typographic errors, this is a useful 16 page
review of the situation. - Mod.MHJ
